query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `industry_benchmarks` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `sector` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `subsector` varchar(255),
  `region` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'Saudi Arabia',
  `month` int NOT NULL,
  `year` int NOT NULL,
  `quarter` int,
  `avg_saudization_rate` int,
  `median_saudization_rate` int,
  `top_quartile_saudization_rate` int,
  `avg_time_to_hire` int,
  `avg_cost_per_hire` int,
  `avg_offer_acceptance_rate` int,
  `avg_retention_rate` int,
  `avg_turnover_rate` int,
  `avg_salary_range` varchar(100),
  `median_salary` int,
  `avg_quality_of_hire` int,
  `avg_candidate_satisfaction` int,
  `total_companies_in_sample` int,
  `data_source` varchar(255),
  `confidence_level` int,
  `notes` text,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `industry_benchmarks_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
